function Start()

	id_Self = Hydra.QuestGetOwner()

	vendralClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(ID_VENDRAL)
	ghostBoyClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(ID_GHOST_BOY)
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(ghostBoyClone) and Hydra.ActorIsValid(ghostBoyClone) then
		Hydra.QActorWait(ghostBoyClone, 1.5)
		Hydra.QActorWait(vendralClone, 1.5)
		Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(ghostBoyClone, CONVO_TROST)
		Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(vendralClone, CONVO_TROST)
		Hydra.QActorWait(ghostBoyClone, 1.5)
		Hydra.QActorWait(vendralClone, 1.5)
		Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(ghostBoyClone, 1)
		Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(vendralClone, 0)
		Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(CONVO_TROST, id_Self, ghostBoyClone, vendralClone)
	end
	
end

function Start(idActor, fRange, idActorDetector)
	id_Self = Hydra.QuestGetOwner()
	Hydra.QActorPlaySimpleConversation(CONVO_GHOST, idActor)
end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
	id_Self = Hydra.QuestGetOwner()
	
	--Clone Actions
	actorClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(ID_VENDRAL)
	if (Hydra.ActorIsValid(actorClone)) then	
		Hydra.QActorWait(actorClone, 0.5)
		Hydra.QActorPlayConversation(CONVO_VENDRAL_03, id_Self, actorClone)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(actorClone, LOC_VENDRAL_END, "NPC_WALK", true)
		Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(actorClone, 1)
	end
	
end
